                            <comment id="412001" author="JIRAUSER19217" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:42:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adilger&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adilger&quot;&gt;adilger&lt;/a&gt; !&lt;br/&gt;
The patch successfully pushed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/54862&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/54862&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="411999" author="adilger" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:30:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=skoyama&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;skoyama&quot;&gt;skoyama&lt;/a&gt;, can you please try again.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="411997" author="JIRAUSER19217" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2024 01:12:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After setting up git hooks, I was able to execute `git commit -avs`.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
commit 0dad31e0b99c5ba5f8714faf3aad95a785e15c6b (HEAD -&amp;gt; skoyama/fix-typo)
Author: Sohei Koyama &amp;lt;skoyama@ddn.com&amp;gt;
Date: &#160; Mon Apr 22 09:55:17 2024 +0900

&#160; &#160; LU-928 misc: fix typos &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; comments
&#160; &#160;&#160;
&#160; &#160; Fix typo obejct -&amp;gt; object.
&#160; &#160;&#160;
&#160; &#160; Signed-off-by: Sohei Koyama &amp;lt;skoyama@ddn.com&amp;gt;
&#160; &#160; Change-Id: I4ab626ca188166e439191450b48e394243116bef
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And, `ssh -p 29418 review.whamcloud.com test` returns &quot;&lt;tt&gt;fatal: Gerrit Code Review: test: not found&quot;.&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
%  ssh -p 29418 review.whamcloud.com test
Enter passphrase &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; key &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/skoyama/.ssh/id_ed25519&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: 
fatal: Gerrit Code Review: test: not found
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then, push to the Gerrit (not /fs/lustre/release but fs/lustre-release, right?), it failed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
% git push -v ssh://skoyama@review.whamcloud.com:29418/fs/lustre-release HEAD:refs/&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;/master
Pushing to ssh://review.whamcloud.com:29418/fs/lustre-release
Enter passphrase &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; key &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/skoyama/.ssh/id_ed25519&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: 
fatal: Upload denied &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; project &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&apos;fs/lustre-release&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
fatal: Could not read from remote repository.

Please make sure you have the correct access rights
and the repository exists. 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="411993" author="adilger" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:42:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=skoyama&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;skoyama&quot;&gt;skoyama&lt;/a&gt;, you don&apos;t need to be part of the submitters group to push a new patch, that is only needed for landing patches. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Things to check:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;almost all new patches should be submitted to &lt;tt&gt;&lt;b&gt;fs&lt;/b&gt;/lustre-release&lt;/tt&gt; on the master branch. Backporting to maintenance release will depend on the nature of the patch, but generally a cleanup like this that is only fixing internal comments and test scripts would not be backported to a release branch&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;check that you have the Git commit hooks installed, so that your patch has a &quot;&lt;tt&gt;Change-Id:&lt;/tt&gt; line and the commit message format follow the correct style.
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# cd .git/hooks
# ln -sf ../../contrib/git-hooks/*commit-msg .
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;check that you are pushing to port 29428 on &lt;tt&gt;review.whamcloud.com&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;check that your SSH key is installed properly to your account. You should be able to run &quot;&lt;tt&gt;ssh -p 29418 review.whamcloud.com test&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; and it Gerrit will reply &quot;&lt;tt&gt;fatal: Gerrit Code Review: test: not found&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; if it is working and another error like &quot;&lt;tt&gt;review.whamcloud.com: Permission denied (publickey).&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; if you are using the wrong username or your SSH key is not working.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Please see the &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/Using_Gerrit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Using Gerrit&lt;/a&gt; page for full details&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="411992" author="JIRAUSER19217" created="Sun, 21 Apr 2024 23:45:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Andreas&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll try to use &lt;del&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-928&quot; title=&quot;Update or improvement to a code comment&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-928&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-928&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have plans to send a patch, but cannot push to Gerrit. Maybe because skoyama (me) don&apos;t belong to lustre-submitters group.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="411985" author="adilger" created="Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:14:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=skoyama&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;skoyama&quot;&gt;skoyama&lt;/a&gt; are you planning to push a patch to fix this yourself, or are you only reporting the error?  A quick search shows this same error in several places, in comments or test scripts, but not in any user messages.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="411984" author="adilger" created="Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:08:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No need to file a separate ticket for every minor spelling fix. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please use &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-928&quot; title=&quot;Update or improvement to a code comment&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-928&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-928&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for this. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
